{"tid":562902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲廢老坐小巴係都唔死入去","createTime":"2018-02-16T11:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T11:38:10.000Z","uid":131293,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f588f5e57ff2ec34818ef1c541939c6c8871a6","tid":562902,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"最近發現 坐咗廿年小巴 啲廢老係都要坐出面<br />\n有一種講唔出嘅執念<br />\n頂鳩住哂 明明入面仲有位<br />\n你攞得多嘢都算 你乜春都冇攞就死入去啦<br />\n當你想入去坐入面個位嘅時候<br />\n佢哋又啤鳩你 好似唔想你坐入去咁<br />\n屌你老母2蚊大哂？ 我俾得多過你㗎<br />\n是咁的 今日咁啱就成車得翻一個位<br />\n又係感 得翻入面個位 個廢老就係出面個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/185802_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F185802_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5fafd706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐坐下都冇乜嘢 一望過去<br />\n隻腳掂唔到車底 要攞隻腳頂住前面凳尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: red;\">借力</span><br />\n真係鄧前面條友慘 成程都俾人頂住<br />\n好好哋坐入面咪冇嘢囉 何必要咁樣自曝其短呢<br />\n我本身都唔想笑柒你 最尾都忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過諗深一層 可能佢少林寺出嚟<br />\n隻腳咁樣垂直用力搭幾個字車都Hold得住<br />\n呢個腳力 唔撚係講笑"},{"pid":"68e0aaff36535f6e618aba3ca0687d3eb76aab45","tid":562902,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34655f2c956ecc7a51d5d590de70cf7b85332a12","tid":562902,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"廢老坐入面落車唔方便 就算早上車都要坐出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f077dd02043da3d14c6ad126c3f62c8a0b84eb7","tid":562902,"uid":22382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"如果夠高坐出面都冇乜野 但拎隻腳頂住前面真係好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039ab92318c6a985e64a14f1